<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I only read The Don and Gadfly so my answer is for these two. They both have historic theme but very very different. They belong to one genre that&apos;s a<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I only read The Don and Gadfly so my answer is for these two. They both have historic theme but very very different. They belong to one genre that's all. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
